    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/de0d61d0d53176545cb84f04d2e48888.poster.avif?t=1757036132\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/de0d61d0d53176545cb84f04d2e48888.webm?t=1757036132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/de0d61d0d53176545cb84f04d2e48888.mp4?t=1757036132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Poppy Sanctum is a single-player puzzle/adventure game</strong> set in the fantasy world of Spectra. A place of magic, mages, and red pandas.</h2><br><strong>Explore the sanctum of the emerald highlands as MIMI.</strong><br><br>A cause and effect, physics-platformer with a focus on mystery and world-building.<br>You control a small red panda who will climb, run, swim, and traverse a hand-crafted landscape of puzzles.<br><br>Pairing up with other creatures to help solve these puzzles by conducting various magics: Gravity, Energy, and Essentia (a dark magic). You'll need to replenish your stamina with apples, bugs, and other treats that red pandas love.<br><br>In this labyrinth you'll avoid volunteer keepers, and poachers who break into the sanctum.<br><br>This brief adventure will delight those who love cozy games with satisfying <i>chill-zones</i> of the forest and oceans.<br>You can choose to stay in the sanctum and keep MIMI healthy, or escape for home.<br><br><strong>Getting to know friends is the only way out of this tomb.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/79831dee448b9443ab6ba21108e9d4c9.avif?t=1757036132\" width=616 height=406 /></span><br><br><strong>For millennia Popignis have survived thanks to their energy-conductive pelt. An adaptation rarely seen in Spectra.</strong><br>This brilliant creature, dubbed Poppy resides in the emerald Sanctum of the great highlands...<br><br>A <strong>Poppy sanctuary</strong> was established by the second king of Spectra.<br><br>For some, this is a beautiful home... However dark mysteries reside.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/7f5b4823e46dda0f819cc22b47fb55ca.poster.avif?t=1757036132\" width=616 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/7f5b4823e46dda0f819cc22b47fb55ca.webm?t=1757036132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/7f5b4823e46dda0f819cc22b47fb55ca.mp4?t=1757036132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/d7f1c9b917955d73096041428e974e24.avif?t=1757036132\" width=616 height=430 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/f9633a20d8276759590e7a7cadd921ef.poster.avif?t=1757036132\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/f9633a20d8276759590e7a7cadd921ef.webm?t=1757036132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/f9633a20d8276759590e7a7cadd921ef.mp4?t=1757036132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840250/extras/b3ef454425f8f552f